com.esri.mo2.cs.geod
Interface ReferencedCoordinateSystem

All Superinterfaces:
Cloneable, CoordinateSystem, Equivalency, GeodeticObject, NamedObject
All Known Implementing Classes:
ReferencedCoordinateSystemImpl
public interface ReferencedCoordinateSystem
extends NamedObject, GeodeticObject, CoordinateSystem

Represents a coordinate system geo-referenced to WGS84 by datum transformation, thus a point in any ReferencedCoordinateSystem can be transformed to any other ReferencedCoordinateSystem. Conceptually a ReferencedCoordinateSystem consists of a ReferencedDatum, PrimeMeridian and a Projection. It has a identifying name, description, and long description.

See Also:
ReferencedDatum, PrimeMeridian, Projection
